text: Sepp Lichtenegger (born 13 November 1937) is an Austrian ski jumper. He competed at the 1964 Winter Olympics and the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Austria Category:Ski jumpers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:People from Gmunden District Category:Sportspeople from Upper Austria
